It&#x27;s done in CSS3 + JS, so it should be pretty easy.<p><a href="https://desandro.github.io/3dtransforms/examples/card-01.html" rel="nofollow">https://desandro.github.io/3dtransforms/examples/card-01.htm...</a><p>#card.flipped {
      -webkit-transform: rotateY( 180deg );
         -moz-transform: rotateY( 180deg );
           -o-transform: rotateY( 180deg );
              transform: rotateY( 180deg );
    }
